Feature brainstorm session - Q1 2024

Attendees: Sarah, Mike, Jennifer

Main ideas:
1. Smart tagging system
   - Auto-suggest tags based on content
   - Custom tag colors
   - Tag hierarchy (parent/child)
   
2. Collaboration features
   - Real-time editing
   - Comments and mentions
   - Version history
   - Permission levels (viewer, editor, admin)
   
3. Automation
   - Recurring tasks
   - Auto-archive old items
   - Notifications and reminders
   - Integration triggers (when X happens, do Y)
   
4. Analytics dashboard
   - Usage metrics
   - Team productivity stats
   - Trend analysis
   - Export reports

Concerns raised:
- Performance with large datasets
- Mobile experience needs work
- Pricing unclear for enterprise

Next steps:
- Prioritize top 3 features
- Get user feedback on mockups
- Estimate engineering effort
- Review with leadership

Meeting adjourned: 4:30pm
